$NetBSD: patch-makefile,v 1.2 2022/12/11 20:28:09 rhialto Exp $

Fix png16 detection.
Let INCLUDES and LIBRARIES be the sole source for INCPATH and LIBPATH,
to avoid seeing non-pkgsrc libraries (except MacOS platform).

